      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "**Module Title: Global Dynamics Workplace Etiquette**\n\n**1. Email Etiquette**\nAlways communicate with **respect** and clarity, ensuring your tone remains **professional** even during disagreements. Strictly adhere to **boundaries** by responding within 24 hours and never using all-caps or slang in formal correspondence.\n\n**2. Office and Common Area Conduct**\nRespect **boundaries** by keeping noise levels low in shared spaces and never blocking walkways or workstations. Maintain **professionalism** by cleaning up after yourself and using headphones to protect auditory **boundaries** for colleagues.\n\n**3. Meeting Behavior**\nEnter meetings with **respect** for everyone's time, start promptly, and end on schedule to demonstrate **professionalism**. Clearly define **boundaries** by staying on topic and using the chat function for non-urgent questions rather than interrupting speakers.\n\n**Conclusion**\nBy consistently applying **respect**, **boundaries**, and **professionalism** in every interaction, we foster a safe and productive environment for all Global Dynamics employees.",
      "source": "target",
